publicwhip.spmotion: *S2M-3794 Donald Gorrie on behalf of the Procedures Committee: Private Bill Committee Assessors—That the Parliament notes the Procedures Committee’s 1st Report, 2006 (Session 2), Private Bill Committee assessors (SP Paper 481), and agrees that the changes to Standing Orders set out in Annexe A to the report be made with effect from 19 January 2006. Supported by: Karen Gillon*
